{"tid":2206729,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"解散IT User Team","createTime":"2020-09-17T16:07:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T04:50:35.000Z","uid":356414,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0175bfd35ad77fad5577f376c126e7953b37f76f","tid":2206729,"uid":356414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T16:07:05.000Z","msg":"IT User Team？<br />\n<br />\n據朋友所言，<br />\n<br />\n他在大公司IT部門，<br />\n<br />\n近期開左一條冗員大Team，<br />\n<br />\n叫User Team<br />\n<br />\n要管理Project和作User 及IT中間人。<br />\n<br />\n而呢個部門，<br />\n<br />\n由一d 無能人士請左班無PM經驗，<br />\n<br />\n又無IT tech <br />\n<br />\n態度又有問題的靚仔靚妹入黎做，<br />\n<br />\n懷疑呢條Team manager <br />\n<br />\n見小鮮肉後生靚女就請，<br />\n<br />\n聽教聽話而控制，<br />\n<br />\n做花瓶一流，<br />\n<br />\n只係聽指令，<br />\n<br />\n幫廢物上司打小報告。<br />\n<br />\n他們有N宗罪，<br />\n<br />\n1. 做Forwarder<br />\n<br />\n將User 的requirement 搬事過紙，<br />\n<br />\n不經思考分析，forward 連正常人都覺得有問題的requirement （兩份不同report defintion 但同一份requirement）給tech。<br />\n<br />\nTech 嘈果班BA，他們一句話我地跟指令做野。果然嘆為觀止。<br />\n<br />\n2.應跟的不跟<br />\n<br />\nBA 講完requirements後，<br />\n<br />\nUser 和Tech 要自己聯絡，<br />\n<br />\n一概不理。<br />\n<br />\n大家都覺得資料不足，<br />\n<br />\n找他們時，一律不覆，無理過。<br />\n<br />\n等BA被User 逼迫時，先去做野，<br />\n<br />\n結果Tech 做到隻狗甘，<br />\n<br />\n我朋友認為是人禍。<br />\n<br />\n話時話，識得做得野的BA，都嘆息一番，<br />\n<br />\n公司命運裁在這班冗員手上，有前途可言嗎？<br />\n<br />\n聽完朋友講，這班人是浪費公司資源。"},{"pid":"f36d3e3ed74a4517864126b0edcbea38e66ef8d4","tid":2206729,"uid":16069,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T16:18:29.000Z","msg":"公司名？"},{"pid":"f8f893f751aaccf237472cb72714698a02325794","tid":2206729,"uid":356414,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f36d3e3ed74a4517864126b0edcbea38e66ef8d4","tid":2206729,"uid":16069,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T16:18:29.000Z","msg":"公司名？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:34:15.000Z","msg":"某大地產集團，屬下公司"},{"pid":"dbc4184194d5434254195aacbc5b8ad6ac506fd9","tid":2206729,"uid":53798,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T04:04:16.000Z","msg":"BA就BA啦, IT user team咁on9"},{"pid":"f8453acd2169eeccff1142c03b5de81eda4f96c7","tid":2206729,"uid":356414,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbc4184194d5434254195aacbc5b8ad6ac506fd9","tid":2206729,"uid":53798,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T04:04:16.000Z","msg":"BA就BA啦, IT user team咁on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T04:50:35.000Z","msg":"都係叫BA，但無腦果隻。<br />\n<br />\n又不tech，又無business logic，<br />\n<br />\n淨係識admin ticketing system。<br />\n<br />\n我豆埋他們份糧。"}],"pinned":{"pid":"dbc4184194d5434254195aacbc5b8ad6ac506fd9","tid":2206729,"uid":53798,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T04:04:16.000Z","msg":"BA就BA啦, IT user team咁on9"}}